'''秦岭细鳞鲑'''（学名：''Brachymystax lenok tsinlingensis''）也称'''花鱼'''、'''梅花鱼'''、'''金板鱼'''、'''闾花鱼'''、'''五色鱼'''、'''闾鱼'''等，是[[细鳞鲑|细鳞鲑]]的一个[[亚种|亚种]]<ref>{{zh}}[[李思忠_(鱼类学家)|李思忠]]，[http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-DWFL196601012.htm 陕西太白山细鳞鲑的一新亚种] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cnki.com.cn/Article/CJFDTOTAL-DWFL196601012.htm |date=20140811233833 }}. [[动物分类学报|动物分类学报]]，1966年01期</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://museum.ioz.ac.cn/topic_detail.aspx?id=230 |title=中国重要物种资源－鱼类：秦岭细鳞鲑 Brachymystax lenok tsinlingensis |access-date=2017-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708110135/http://museum.ioz.ac.cn/topic_detail.aspx?id=230 |archive-date=2018-07-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。 为[[中国|中国]]的[[特有种|特有种]]，主要分布于[[秦岭|秦岭]]两侧[[渭河|渭河]]上游及其支流及[[汉水|汉水]]北侧支流[[湑水河|湑水河]]、[[子午河|子午河]]上游的溪流中。<ref>[https://new.qq.com/omn/20190514/20190514A0N8C6.html 秦岭野生保护动物——细鳞鲑]</ref>  秦岭细鳞鲑是典型的[[第四纪冰川|第四纪冰川]]陆封残留冷水性鱼类<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://article.hongxiu.com/a/2011-12-2/4104717.shtml |title=大海遗子——秦岭细鳞鲑 |access-date=2011-12-19 |archive-date=2015-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622174410/http://article.hongxiu.com/a/2011-12-2/4104717.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，现为[[中国国家重点保护野生动物名录|中国国家二级保护野生动物]]<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 宝鸡新闻网 | title = 秦岭细鳞鲑人工孵化首次取得成功 | url = http://www.baojinews.com/_info/content_163921.htm | date = 2010-05-27 | accessdate = 2011-02-23 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201114548/http://www.baojinews.com/_info/content_163921.htm | archivedate = 2014-02-01 | df =  }}</ref>。目前在[[陕西省|陕西省]]和[[甘肃省|甘肃省]]都设有保护秦岭细鳞鲑自然保护区<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 新华网 | title =中国成立首个保护秦岭细鳞鲑国家级自然保护区| url = http://news.xinhuanet.com/politics/2009-11/29/content_12558658.htm| date = 2009-11-29 | accessdate = 2011-02-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 中国甘肃网 | title = 漳县秦岭细鳞鲑自然保护区向“国家级”晋升 | url = http://www.gscn.com.cn/pub/gansu/sszh/2010/05/13/1273708307620.html | date = 2010-05-13 | accessdate = 2011-02-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150622200017/http://www.gscn.com.cn/pub/gansu/sszh/2010/05/13/1273708307620.html | archive-date = 2015-06-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

鱼类学者中间对于秦岭细鳞鲑是否为独立的[[细鳞鲑|细鳞鲑]][[亚种|亚种]]，观点有一定分歧。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://wfmed.pfizermedicalinformation.cn/Paper/Detail/PeriodicalPaper_ssswxb201803013 |title=基于形态学差异探讨秦岭细鳞鲑亚种有效性问题 |access-date=2018-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180708104320/https://wfmed.pfizermedicalinformation.cn/Paper/Detail/PeriodicalPaper_ssswxb201803013 |archive-date=2018-07-08 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>近年文献资料表明，秦岭细鳞鲑可被视为[[细鳞鲑属|细鳞鲑属]]的一个有效[[物种|种]]（而不仅仅为细鳞鲑亚种）；其分布范围不仅限于秦岭：韩国等国外学者将韩国的细鳞鲑种群也归入了秦岭细鳞鲑。<ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = 世界银行 | title = Fishes of Mongolia | url = http://siteresources.worldbank.org/INTEAPREGTOPENVIRONMENT/Resources/fishes_of_mongolia.pdf | date = 2006-09 | accessdate = 2014-12-07 | archive-date = 2016-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160114200459/http://siteresources.worldbank.org/INTEAPREGTOPENVIRONMENT/Resources/fishes_of_mongolia.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/226775236_Threatened_fishes_of_the_world_Brachymystax_lenok_tsinlingensis_Li_1966_Salmonidae |title=Threatened fishes of the world: Brachymystax lenok tsinlingensis Li, 1966 (Salmonidae) |accessdate=2016-06-09 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305002802/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/226775236_Threatened_fishes_of_the_world_Brachymystax_lenok_tsinlingensis_Li_1966_Salmonidae |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | language = en | publisher = Zootaxa | title = Revalidation and redescription of B. tsinlingensis Li, 1966 from China | url = http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2015/f/zt03962p205.pdf | date = 2015-05-22 | accessdate = 2015-06-22 | archive-date = 2015-06-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150622174449/http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2015/f/zt03962p205.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://species.nibr.go.kr/endangeredspecies/rehome/exlist/exlist_view.jsp?link_gbn=ex_search&rlcls_sno=323 |title=Endangered species of Korea: Brachymystax lenok tsinlingensis Li |accessdate=2018-03-18 |archive-date=2018-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319084704/https://species.nibr.go.kr/endangeredspecies/rehome/exlist/exlist_view.jsp?link_gbn=ex_search&rlcls_sno=323 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此鱼为中国[[国家重点保护野生动物名录|国家重点保护野生动物名录]][[鱼纲|鱼纲]]（1988年版）15种野生[[硬骨鱼类|硬骨鱼类]]中，唯一于1949年以后命名的珍稀鱼类
<ref>2021年公布的新版[[国家重点保护野生动物名录|国家重点保护野生动物名录]]已将受保护野生硬骨鱼类增为[https://birdingbeijing.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/2021-List-of-Class-I-and-Class-II-protected-species-in-China-annotated.xls  83种（或属）]，收录包括[[细鳞鲑属|细鳞鲑属]]所有野外种群及自1960年代以来发现的[[小体高原鳅|小体高原鳅]]、[[稀有鮈鲫|稀有鮈鲫]]、[[裸腹盲魮|裸腹盲魮]]、[[黄线薄鳅|黄线薄鳅]]、[[湘西盲南鳅|湘西盲南鳅]]、[[厚唇原吸鳅|厚唇原吸鳅]]、[[長絲黑鮡|長絲黑鮡]]等。</ref>； 它与[[櫻花鉤吻鮭|櫻花鉤吻鮭]]及[[川陕哲罗鲑|川陕哲罗鲑]]类似，是冰川期来自北方、孑遗于东亚暖温带而[[异域物种形成|演化形成]]的鲑科鱼类物种<ref>{{cite journal|author=李思忠|title=中国鲑科鱼类地理分布的探讨|journal=动物学杂志|year=1984|issue=1|url=http://dwxzz.ioz.ac.cn/ch/reader/view_abstract.aspx?file_no=84010034|access-date=2018-06-07|archive-date=2018-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524222143/http://dwxzz.ioz.ac.cn/ch/reader/view_abstract.aspx?file_no=84010034|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

